A car can drive through a wall, yes, but not that of a battle cruiser 
that is designed to take hits from other battle cruisers. A simple 
hit against an IF wall would do more damage to the car than the wall.

And the autoguns are firing from pretty much all directions, Havoc 
won't be big enough to block them all.
